creator: LoungeUp
descriptionHtml:
Make the most of your skiing holiday in the Alps and your stay at Les Balcons thanks to our application!

Check-in online in advance to save you time on arrival. Discover and book services available at your residence. Take advantage of all our useful information for your stay. Constantly be in touch with our team. Book your next stay in the Alps…

For more than 25 years, Les Balcons has welcomed you to its internationally renowned resorts.
Our vision is to offer you the best of the mountain:
* Dream locations with magnificent panoramic views
* Village style residences and hotels including shops and restaurants designed to make your holiday easier
* Wide range of rooms and apartments tailored to your holiday as a couple, family or group of friends
* Well-being services, a high-quality welcome and a commitment to the environment
descriptionShort: Chalets, Résidences, Hôtels & Spas en Savoie

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
We are updating our app to enhance your experience.
Update to take advantage of the latest features and fixes.
